Description: Agentic-first CLI successor to dd with GUI/TUI
 AgenticBlockTransfer (abt) is a cross-platform disk image writer
 with CLI, TUI, and GUI modes. It provides safe, verified block-level
 writes with AI-discoverable ontology, multi-format support (ISO, IMG,
 QCOW2, VHD, VMDK, WIM), auto-decompression, device cloning, secure
 erase, multicast imaging, multi-boot USB, and more.
 .
 Features: pre-flight safety checks, dry-run mode, device fingerprints,
 structured exit codes, partition table backup, MCP server mode,
 localization, accessibility, and WCAG 2.1 AA compliance.
